{"tid":1041701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「亞洲四小龍之首卻鬼混20多年」　韓國瑜嘆：台灣退步得讓人無法接受","createTime":"2019-03-01T04:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T12:56:58.000Z","uid":47714,"like":7,"dislike":110,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"6c97475f73a7cafb8998378b9488f8f58099c543","tid":1041701,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/945379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F945379&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=26585aa5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/945379</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2019/02/14/20190214-054038_U14794_M498707_5e44.jpg?itok=eZM8q1VJ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2019%2F02%2F14%2F20190214-054038_U14794_M498707_5e44.jpg%3Fitok%3DeZM8q1VJ&h=4f0f7102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜今（14）日出席「南方崛起 創赴高雄」產業論壇，在致詞中他表示，市政府應為其他359行做牛做馬，不能作威作福，團隊官員不可有「蒙面大盜」的心態，所有改變就從高雄做起。他也感嘆台灣原為亞洲四小龍之首，但卻一直在退步，讓人無法接受。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜以埃及金字塔為例，說政治人物往往在金字塔的頂端，上任後必須倒過來，市政府應該改變心態，定位在最底層來服務其他359行，「要做牛做馬、不能作威作福」，和企業界做好朋友。他更進一步指出，團隊官員不可以有蒙面大盜「此路為我開，若從此路走，請留買路錢」的心態，要努力協助企業，吸引更多人到高雄投資，創造商機和就業機會。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜最後更批評，台灣原是亞洲四小龍之首，卻整整鬼混了20年，現在回頭來看「國家有進步嗎？有傲人成績嗎？」讓人無法接受，並說「我們一定要重新開始做，就從高雄！」"},{"pid":"5f5b852f0dbf3bd76030a6214c5a632bd251eba0","tid":1041701,"uid":191926,"like":473,"dislike":0,"score":473,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"台灣<br />\n<br />\n四小龍之首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5ec25b9a346721ef7e8d0a2507a3d2f7c45f0b","tid":1041701,"uid":212246,"like":213,"dislike":1,"score":212,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/75309.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F75309.jpg&h=7137eed2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"988245d99c31b008fb6bdc6adb0c5eb56c5b650c","tid":1041701,"uid":39710,"like":170,"dislike":0,"score":170,"quote":{"pid":"5f5b852f0dbf3bd76030a6214c5a632bd251eba0","tid":1041701,"uid":191926,"like":473,"dislike":0,"score":473,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"台灣<br />\n<br />\n四小龍之首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"條友係咪唔識分之一同之首"},{"pid":"abaf4e2e60c110fc5468e42e3246891037bd77c5","tid":1041701,"uid":14816,"like":209,"dislike":0,"score":209,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:54:31.000Z","msg":"台灣幾時做過四小龍之首<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eafca7fa45f3df06d3a53cacc4d3603b6e1a2b3","tid":1041701,"uid":10757,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:55:14.000Z","msg":"四小龍之首<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed805968dbc2304c926658caf1f6a69cc1a8b7a7","tid":1041701,"uid":33907,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:55:29.000Z","msg":"四小蟲之首咋"},{"pid":"fece9eafae638deacd88d1e489a7828f4e00514f","tid":1041701,"uid":41818,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:55:38.000Z","msg":"台狗成日提四小龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc56ef53227836a9d7cc30a82645afcf7e8b828c","tid":1041701,"uid":155902,"like":120,"dislike":1,"score":119,"quote":{"pid":"fece9eafae638deacd88d1e489a7828f4e00514f","tid":1041701,"uid":41818,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:55:38.000Z","msg":"台狗成日提四小龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"仲四小龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.